01:54:34,668 --> 01:54:35,959
"Yes, I am."

746
01:54:36,126 --> 01:54:41,126
"You are the charming one."

747
01:54:42,293 --> 01:54:45,126
"Don't shoot me
with love daggers."

748
01:54:45,293 --> 01:54:47,626
"Please listen to me, my love."

749
01:54:48,376 --> 01:54:51,126
