they will kill every
innocent child

762
01:57:46,293 --> 01:57:49,376
and violate every woman.

763
01:57:50,543 --> 01:57:53,251
They will destroy
and burn everything.

764
01:57:54,376 --> 01:57:57,209
This talk might scare
some small kingdoms.

765
01:57:57,543 --> 01:57:59,376
We have a standing
army of 25,000 soldiers.

766
01:57:59,543 --> 01:58:00,876
Why should we be scared?

767
