02:05:46,668 --> 02:05:48,626
I heard that you promised
both your sons that

857
02:05:48,793 --> 02:05:51,334
the one who kills me
would be made king.

858
02:05:56,793 --> 02:05:59,501
And if both of them
die at my hands?

859
02:06:16,876 --> 02:06:19,501
I will conquer you
and your kingdom

860
02:06:19,668 --> 02:06:20,959
